For anyone wondering If we'll get to see more of this author's work, we won't as Irodori has taken down the English translations for this author in the page where N-hentai gets the galleries (E-hentai, this page is where almost every single translation for h-manga comes out from, as scanlation groups post their work there, and also explains why you see sometimes reposted galleries of certain works, they are just updated versions with minor corrections of the translators/editors, N-hentai does not have this system). If you didn't know the owner of Irodori sells translated versions of some h-manga but also sells pirated works (a horrible double standard)  and is slowly taking over the distribution rights of several authors. If you care about your h-manga and would like to see more translated works, spread the word about the shit site that is Irodori and the piece of shit that is his owner Takahashi.
